(716, 0, '_transient_dash_de3249c4736ad3bd2cd29147c4a0d43e', '<h4>Beliebt</h4>\n<h5><a href=''http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/gtranslate/''>GTranslate</a></h5>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=''plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=gtranslate&amp;_wpnonce=7fbe2c30b0&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800'' class=''thickbox'' title=''GTranslate''>Jetzt installieren</a>)</span>\n<p>Get translations with a single click between 58 languages (more than 98% of internet users) on your website!</p>\n<h4>Neue Plugins</h4>\n<h5><a href=''http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/simple-custo-taxo/''>Simple-Custo-Taxo (Simple Custom Taxonomy)</a></h5>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=''plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=simple-custo-taxo&amp;_wpnonce=6258f36ec5&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800'' class=''thickbox'' title=''Simple-Custo-Taxo (Simple Custom Taxonomy)''>Jetzt installieren</a>)</span>\n<p>version: 1.0\n\nAdds an extra taxonomy option for your posts and add to your site by using the widget in your sidebar.</p>\n<h4>Frisch aktualisiert</h4>\n<h5><a href=''http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/wp-e-commerce-simple-product-options/''>WP e-Commerce Simple Product Options</a></h5>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=''plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=wp-e-commerce-simple-product-options&amp;_wpnonce=78d0a185a4&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800'' class=''thickbox'' title=''WP e-Commerce Simple Product Options''>Jetzt installieren</a>)</span>\n<p>WP e-Commerce extension that allows you to add simple &quot;product options&quot; to products without having to create or manage variations</p>\n', 'no'),
